## Verification

### Phase 1
```bash
# Full tree
bun run dev help --json | jq '.routes | length'  # Should show all route groups

# Specific command
bun run dev help --json issue list | jq '.flags[].name'  # Should show limit, query, etc.

# Specific group
bun run dev help --json issue | jq '.commands[].path'  # Should list all issue subcommands

# Human mode unchanged
bun run dev help  # Should show branded banner as before
bun run dev help issue list  # Should show Stricli help as before

# Tests
bun test test/lib/introspect.test.ts
bun test test/lib/introspect.property.test.ts
bun test test/commands/help.test.ts

# Verify generate-skill still works
bun run script/generate-skill.ts
```

